|----------|-------|-------|
| ¬V P0 | `visual-investigation-p0` | R-PRI1 |
| V ∧ ¬G | `gsettings-deep-pass` | R-PRI2 |
| G ∧ ¬Vc | `capsule-captures` | R-PRI2b |
